ONE OF CANADA'S
TOP BUSINESS SCHOOLS

00:05.038 --> 00:07.174
WITH REALLY GOOD GRADES.

00:07.207 --> 00:10.210
NOW I'M USING MY KNOWLEDGE
TO HELP STRUGGLING

00:10.244 --> 00:13.380
SMALL BUSINESS OWNERS MAKE IT
IN THIS COMPETITIVE WORLD.

00:21.421 --> 00:25.359
THIS IS NATHAN FOR YOU.

00:25.392 --> 00:28.095
THERE'S NOTHING PEOPLE LIKE MORE
THAN BEING SCARED.

00:28.128 --> 00:29.997
- WELL, YEAH, I LIKE MY--
- WOAH!

00:30.030 --> 00:31.231
- OH, MY GOD.

00:31.265 --> 00:32.833
- THAT'S WHY,
WHEN OCTOBER SWINGS AROUND,

00:32.866 --> 00:35.135
HAUNTED HOUSES
ARE BIG BUSINESS.

00:35.169 --> 00:37.804
BRUCE STANTON IS THE OWNER
OF REIGN OF TERROR,

00:37.838 --> 00:41.175
AN ANNUAL HAUNTED HOUSE
IN THOUSAND OAKS, CALIFORNIA.

00:41.208 --> 00:44.011
- WE HAVE A PERFECT ENVIRONMENT
TO SET YOU UP TO BE SCARED.

00:44.044 --> 00:45.479
- BUT AFTER TAKING
A WALK-THROUGH

00:45.512 --> 00:48.048
OF THE SUPPOSEDLY
SCARY MANSION,

00:48.081 --> 00:49.616
I CAME OUT
LESS THAN IMPRESSED.

00:49.650 --> 00:50.918
HI.

00:50.951 --> 00:52.986
SO I TALKED TO BRUCE
ONE ON ONE ABOUT AN IDEA I HAD

00:53.020 --> 00:54.488
TO HELP HIS BUSINESS.

00:54.521 --> 00:57.858
WHAT IS THE BEST PRESS
A HAUNTED HOUSE CAN GET?

00:57.891 --> 01:01.061
- THAT IT'S SO SCARY,
SOMEONE PEED THEIR PANTS.

01:01.094 --> 01:02.663
- NO.

01:02.696 --> 01:04.331
PEE IS ONE THING.

01:04.364 --> 01:06.533
I WANT YOUR HAUNTED HOUSE
TO BE SO SCARY

01:06.567 --> 01:11.505
