FOR BEING TOO SCARY.

01:11.538 --> 01:13.440
- I DON'T KNOW THAT
WE WANT PEOPLE TO SUE US.

01:13.473 --> 01:16.443
- IF THE REIGN OF TERROR
WAS SUED FOR BEING TOO SCARY,

01:16.476 --> 01:18.212
THAT NEWS WOULD
ATTRACT THRILL-SEEKERS

01:18.245 --> 01:19.847
FROM AROUND THE WORLD.

01:19.880 --> 01:22.950
THE PLAN, GET CUSTOMERS TO SUE
BY MAKING THEM THINK

01:22.983 --> 01:25.118
