REALLY GOING TO DIE.

01:25.152 --> 01:28.322
- NO, BECAUSE I THINK
THAT WILL BE GOING TOO FAR.

01:28.355 --> 01:32.359
- WELL, YOUR CURRENT APPROACH
COULD GET PRESS TOO.

01:32.392 --> 01:33.727
- YES.

01:33.760 --> 01:37.097
- BY BEING THE WORLD'S
LEAST SCARY HAUNTED HOUSE.

01:37.097 --> 01:38.599
- UH, I DON'T THINK THAT'S
THE APPROACH WE WANT, BUT--

01:38.632 --> 01:39.766
- WELL, THAT'S THE APPROACH
IT SEEMS LIKE

01:39.800 --> 01:41.134
YOU'RE CURRENTLY TAKING.

01:41.168 --> 01:42.402
- NO, WE ARE A SCARY--

01:42.436 --> 01:45.105
- "REIGN OF TERROR.
WHERE PUSSIES GO TO RELAX."

01:45.138 --> 01:46.473
- OH, OKAY.

01:46.507 --> 01:49.510
- OR, "REIGN OF TERROR,
YOU'RE PROBABLY GOING TO DIE."

01:49.543 --> 01:51.845
- YOU MEAN IN THE HAUNTED HOUSE,
WE PAINT A PICTURE

01:51.879 --> 01:54.915
THAT THEIR DEATH IS...
IMMINENT.

01:54.948 --> 01:56.250
- YES.
- OKAY.

01:56.283 --> 01:58.418
- TO SCARE PEOPLE ENOUGH
THAT THEY WOULD SUE,

01:58.452 --> 02:00.954
