03:06.153 --> 03:07.754
AND I WAS SUPPOSED
TO NOT TOUCH YOU.

03:07.788 --> 03:08.822
- WAIT, SORRY, JUST--
- SORRY.

03:08.856 --> 03:09.823
- CAN YOU GUYS
WAIT IN HERE ONE SEC?

03:09.857 --> 03:11.325
- YEAH.
- SORRY, ONE SECOND.

03:11.358 --> 03:13.060
- WHAT IS IT CALLED?
- IT'S CALLED KLEIN'S DISEASE.

03:13.060 --> 03:14.228
AND IT'S AN IMMUNITY--
