- HELLO.

06:07.267 --> 06:08.302
- PETER--
- PETER.

06:08.335 --> 06:09.503
- PETER MARX.
- MO.

06:09.536 --> 06:10.704
- MO. AND YOU ARE?
- I'M MIRA.

06:10.737 --> 06:12.039
- MIRA.

06:12.039 --> 06:14.208
- SO IF YOU FOUND
THE HAUNTED HOUSE TOO SCARY,

06:14.241 --> 06:16.243
AND YOU WANT TO PRESS
ANY LEGAL ACTION

06:16.276 --> 06:19.346
AGAINST THE HAUNTED HOUSE,
HE CAN TALK TO YOU--

06:19.379 --> 06:21.448
- WE CAN TALK AND SEE--
UNDER THE LAW,

06:21.481 --> 06:24.084
YOU HAVE CLAIMS FOR WHAT WE CALL
"INTENTIONAL INFLICTION

06:24.117 --> 06:25.419
OF EMOTIONAL DISTRESS."

