OR EVEN "NEGLIGENT INFLICTION
OF EMOTIONAL DISTRESS."

06:27.688 --> 06:30.123
I DON'T WANT TO CREATE PROBLEMS
THAT DON'T EXIST,

06:30.157 --> 06:32.726
BUT IF YOU HAVE THOSE CONCERNS,
FEEL FREE TO CALL ME.

06:32.759 --> 06:34.061
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE TO,

06:34.061 --> 06:35.929
IT'S ONLY IF YOU'RE
COMFORTABLE ABOUT IT.

06:35.963 --> 06:38.065
- AFTER RUNNING
SEVERAL MORE CUSTOMERS

06:38.065 --> 06:39.900
THROUGH MY VERSION
OF THE HAUNTED HOUSE--

06:39.933 --> 06:41.068
- HEY, MOM, IT'S JORDAN.

06:41.101 --> 06:43.136
UM, ACTUALLY I HAVE
TO GO TO THE HOSPITAL.

06:43.170 --> 06:45.072
THERE WAS SOMEBODY
WITH A DISEASE.

06:45.105 --> 06:47.107
- NOW, I'M NOT TRYING
TO CREATE A LAWSUIT HERE,

06:47.140 --> 06:50.210
I JUST--YOU HAVE CERTAIN RIGHTS
UNDER CALIFORNIA LAW.

06:50.244 --> 06:52.212
- I PAID BRUCE A VISIT
TO FOLLOW UP.

06:52.246 --> 06:53.680
WHAT DID YOU THINK?

06:53.714 --> 06:56.450
- WELL, I THINK IT'S COMPLETELY
IMPRACTICAL FOR A HAUNTED HOUSE.

06:56.483 --> 06:57.851
- BUT PEOPLE WERE SCARED.

06:57.885 --> 06:59.686
- YEAH, I DON'T KNOW,
I COULDN'T TELL.

06:59.720 --> 07:01.154
- WE HAD A LAWYER
