- HELLO.
- HI, THIS IS BRUCE.

07:07.461 --> 07:09.263
- PETER.
- HE RUNS THE HAUNTED HOUSE.

07:09.296 --> 07:10.397
- NICE TO MEET YOU.

07:10.430 --> 07:11.832
