OKAY.

07:36.190 --> 07:37.958
- WELL, I'M TRYING
TO GET YOU PRESS.

07:38.058 --> 07:39.226
- OKAY.

07:39.259 --> 07:42.062
- IN THE END, THE SCARIEST THING
ABOUT THE HAUNTED HOUSE

07:42.062 --> 07:43.931
WAS BRUCE'S TERRIBLE MANNERS.

07:43.964 --> 07:47.134
BUT WHEN SOMEONE'S RUDE TO YOU,
YOU CAN'T TAKE IT PERSONALLY.

07:47.167 --> 07:49.169
