TO KEEP GOING.

07:52.339 --> 07:54.307
- WHEN YOU LOOK AT ME,
YOU PROBABLY SEE A GUY

07:54.341 --> 07:56.009
WHO HAS IT ALL.

07:56.043 --> 07:58.745
BUT REALLY, THERE'S A LARGE
PART OF ME THAT'S IMMATURE

07:58.779 --> 08:00.347
AND UNDER-DEVELOPED.

08:00.380 --> 08:03.684
ESPECIALLY WHEN
IT COMES TO WOMEN.

08:03.717 --> 08:06.353
EVERY GIRL I LIKED GROWING UP
REJECTED ME.

08:06.386 --> 08:08.455
AND BECAUSE OF THAT,
I'VE GROWN INTO A MAN

08:08.488 --> 08:11.358
WHO'S CHRONICALLY
NERVOUS AROUND WOMEN.

08:11.391 --> 08:13.527
I'M AN EMOTIONAL MIDGET.

08:13.560 --> 08:15.529
NOW, IF SOMEONE CAME TO ME
WITH THIS PROBLEM,

08:15.562 --> 08:18.732
I'D SUGGEST IMMERSION THERAPY,
WHERE YOU OVERWHELM YOURSELF

08:18.765 --> 08:22.169
WITH YOUR FEAR IN ORDER
TO OVERCOME IT.

08:22.202 --> 08:24.071
SO TONIGHT,
TO INSPIRE YOU,

08:24.104 --> 08:27.641
I'M GOING TO ATTEMPT TO OVERCOME
MY FEAR OF THE OPPOSITE SEX

08:27.674 --> 08:32.179
BY DATING NOT ONE,
BUT TEN WOMEN AT THE SAME TIME.

08:32.212 --> 08:35.182
WISH ME LUCK.

