- ARE YOU IN A RELATIONSHIP
RIGHT NOW?

08:51.131 --> 08:52.733
- YES.
- OKAY.

08:52.766 --> 08:53.867
- UM...

08:53.900 --> 08:56.570
- SO--SORRY, NEVER MIND.
