AS A WAY TO BREAK THE ICE

09:21.261 --> 09:22.596
AND SHOW MY PERSONALITY.

09:22.629 --> 09:23.797
- OH.

09:23.830 --> 09:26.266
- I'M JUST TRYING
TO MEET PEOPLE AND--

09:26.266 --> 09:28.068
NO.

09:30.570 --> 09:32.372
I'M JUST DRINKING
MY OWN SMOOTHIE

09:32.406 --> 09:35.509
THAT I BOUGHT FROM HERE.

09:35.542 --> 09:38.812
BUT I LIKE DRINKING MY SMOOTHIE
OUT OF LITTLE CUPS ON A TRAY.

09:38.845 --> 09:43.016
THAT'S HOW I LIKE
TO DRINK MY SMOOTHIE.

09:43.050 --> 09:45.052
OKAY, WELL I THINK I'M ALLOWED
TO DRINK MY SMOOTHIE

09:45.085 --> 09:46.053
WHEREVER I WANT.

