- YOU NEED TO MOVE THIS.

09:49.089 --> 09:50.290
- HEY!
- YOU NEED TO MOVE THIS.

09:50.323 --> 09:52.893
- YOU CANNOT TOUCH MY TRAY,
THAT IS CRAZY.

09:52.926 --> 09:55.462
THE SMOOTHIE THING
WAS TOO GIMMICKY ANYWAYS,

09:55.495 --> 09:57.764
AND IT FELT THE SAME WAY
WHEN I USED A CUTE DOG.

09:57.798 --> 09:59.933
DO YOU LIKE MY DOG?
- YEAH.

09:59.966 --> 10:02.436
- SAY HI.
- HI.

10:02.469 --> 10:04.004
- BUT JUST WHEN
I WAS READY TO QUIT,

10:04.037 --> 10:05.138
IT HIT ME.

10:05.238 --> 10:07.240
I HAD A MAJOR GIRL MAGNET
AT MY DISPOSAL

10:07.274 --> 10:10.310
THAT I WAS TOTALLY IGNORING.

10:10.344 --> 10:12.779
A TELEVISION CREW.

10:12.813 --> 10:14.915
IT WAS A CRAZY IDEA,
BUT MAYBE WOMEN WOULD DATE ME

10:14.948 --> 10:17.651
JUST FOR THE OPPORTUNITY
TO BE ON TV.

10:17.684 --> 10:19.252
I HAD MY SOLUTION.

10:19.286 --> 10:21.588
I WAS GOING TO CREATE
A FAKE REALITY SHOW

10:21.621 --> 10:24.991
IN WHICH TEN WOMEN WOULD VIE
FOR THE HEART OF ONE MAN.

10:25.025 --> 10:25.992
ME.

10:26.026 --> 10:28.495
