19:20.890 --> 19:22.620
- I'M JUST WONDERING.

19:22.620 --> 19:24.230
- BUT OTHERS
WERE HAPPY FOR ME.

19:25.630 --> 19:26.730
THANK YOU.
- YEAH.

19:26.760 --> 19:28.730
- I HAD ACCOMPLISHED
WHAT I SET OUT TO DO,

19:28.760 --> 19:31.330
BUT THERE WAS STILL
ONE THING I HAD TO MAKE RIGHT.

19:31.370 --> 19:34.200
EARLIER, TONY SHARED
A PERSONAL STORY WITH ME.

19:34.240 --> 19:36.640
HAVE YOU EVER HAD A THREESOME?
- I HAVE, YES.

19:36.670 --> 19:38.870
- AND I ACCIDENTALLY
TOLD IT TO SOME OF THE WOMEN.

19:38.910 --> 19:41.340
