- FROM WHAT
YOU KNOW OF.

20:32.930 --> 20:34.760
- OH, YOU'RE NOT?
- NO, I'M A GREAT GUY.

20:34.800 --> 20:36.100
- WHY'D YOU SAY,
"FROM WHAT YOU KNOW OF"?

20:36.130 --> 20:37.370
- WELL, FROM
WHAT YOU KNOW OF ME.

20:37.400 --> 20:38.800
- YEAH, BUT I JUST
CALLED YOU A GREAT GUY.

20:38.830 --> 20:40.030
